Tasks: MD to HTML and HTML to PDF conversion.
Changes:
- Implemented PdfConverter class in pdf_converter_py.py.
- convert_md_to_html uses Pandoc via subprocess.
- convert_html_to_pdf uses Playwright to render HTML and inject CSS.
- Added unit tests in test_pdf_conversion.py.
Why: To replace the Node.js PDF conversion with a Python-native solution.
